  "stem": "<figure class=\"table\"><table border=\"1\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<th style=\"width: 22.8042%; text-align: center;\" scope=\"row\"><math alttext=\"x\"><mi>x</mi>\n</math></th>\n<td style=\"width: 22.8042%; text-align: center;\"><math alttext=\"24\"><mn>24</mn>\n</math></td>\n<td style=\"width: 22.8042%; text-align: center;\"><math alttext=\"30\"><mn>30</mn>\n</math></td>\n<td style=\"width: 22.8042%; text-align: center;\"><math alttext=\"32\"><mn>32</mn>\n</math></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<th style=\"width: 22.8042%; text-align: center;\" scope=\"row\"><math alttext=\"f left parenthesis x right parenthesis\"><mi>f</mi><mfenced><mi>x</mi></mfenced></math></th>\n<td style=\"width: 22.8042%; text-align: center;\"><math alttext=\"negative 8\"><mo>-</mo><mn>8</mn>\n</math></td>\n<td style=\"width: 22.8042%; text-align: center;\"><math alttext=\"negative 8\"><mo>-</mo><mn>8</mn>\n</math></td>\n<td style=\"width: 22.8042%; text-align: center;\"><math alttext=\"8\"><mn>8</mn>\n</math></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table></figure>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">For the quadratic function <math alttext=\"f\"><mi>f</mi>\n</math>, the table shows three values of <math alttext=\"x\"><mi>x</mi>\n</math> and their corresponding values of&nbsp;<math alttext=\"f left parenthesis x right parenthesis\"><mi>f</mi><mfenced><mi>x</mi></mfenced></math>. Which equation defines <math alttext=\"f\"><mi>f</mi>\n</math>?</p>",
